---
import { SITE } from '../lib/site';
import { categories } from '../lib/categories';
---

<footer class="bg-primary text-white/70 mt-16">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-8">
      <div>
        <p class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-2">{SITE.title}</p>
        <p class="text-[12px] leading-relaxed">副業・投資・キャリアのリアルを記録するメディア。<br/>あなたの「新しい一歩」を応援します。</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-white font-medium text-sm mb-3">カテゴリ</p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-[12px]">
          {Object.entries(categories).map(([slug, cat]) => (
            <li><a href={`/category/${slug}/`} class="hover:text-white transition-colors">{cat.name}</a></li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-white font-medium text-sm mb-3">運営者情報</p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-[12px]">
          <li><a href="/about/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">運営者について</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">プライバシーポリシー</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">お問い合わせ</a></li>
          <li><a href="/sitemap-index.xml" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">サイトマップ</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-white font-medium text-sm mb-3">Follow Us</p>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[13px] hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors cursor-pointer">X</span>
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[13px] hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors cursor-pointer">IG</span>
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[13px] hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors cursor-pointer">YT</span>
          <a href="/rss.xml" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[13px] hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors">RSS</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-6 text-center text-[11px] text-white/40">
      <p class="mb-2">当サイトの情報は個人の調査に基づくものであり、特定の投資や副業を推奨するものではありません。</p>
      &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} {SITE.title}. All Rights Reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
